SPELL E Iron Charge - Physical
Xarofos charge foward in a line, dealing insane amount of damage, they will be ministun for 0.2 but if they are Stun by Iron Blast it
will increase its stun duration and while they are stun, they will lose insane amount of armor, Xarofos will gain insane amount of armor 
while he is Charging and will last for 3 seconds after he is done charging, Each enemys hit will grant him bonus health regeneration
that last 7 seconds. When they get stun by Iron Blast and then by Iron Charge, it will refresh that stun duration, the coldown will
reduce by 0.5 for every auto attack done.

damage 20 25 30 35 plus 10% 20% 30% 40% of Strenght
increase damage 10 20 30 40 plus 25% of strenght
armor lost 7 14 21 28 while stun
increase stun duration 0.4 0.6 0.8 1.0
increase armor while in charge 12 20 28 36
health regeneration per enemy hit 0.9 1.8 2.7 3.6
coldown 30 29 28 27
mana cost 60 80 100 120


talent level 20 upgrade Iron Charge
increase the damage when stun by 20
increase the scaling strenght when stun by 25%
Increase Stun duration by 0.2
increase armor gain while in charge by 10
increase health regeneration gain per hit 0.8
reduce coldown by 4
increase mana cost by 45

add a new modifier Holy Charge
While he is Charging, he will Ignore all form of range attacks and reflect them back at them, those range attack reflected will only
deal 25% of its damage and effect, if Xarofos pass on any allys when Charging, he will heal them by 10% of their max health and give
them 35% of the armor he gain when he is charging for 9 seconds, Upon finishing the charge at the target location, he will cast Iron
Blast with all of its effect and dealing 20% increase damage as well, enemys will also be force to attack him for 2.5 seconds and for
the duration they attack him, they will do 40% less damage to him, Each enemys hit with Iron Charge will increase its base damage by 1
up to 20 bonus damage, at 12 bonus damage Xarofos will gain 12% magic resistence and 80 movespeed also gaining Phase, With the Phase
bonus buff, he will deal 30% of his strenght into damage when he pass inside of enemys and slowing them by 80% for 1.5 seconds, can only
happen every 5 seconds, work with the charge as well, Xarofos will lose 5 stacks if he doesnt hit anyone, he will also lose 1 stack every
time he gets slow.


PASSIVE D OR F Infuse Iron Body (damage return work like return passive from centaur)
Increase Xarofos health and armor, Xarofos will also Reflect damage he takes to his attacker spell or normal attacks, he will also
gain some health regeneration every time he gets hit and having a short duration but refreshing upon getting a new stack of health
regeneration, he also increase all source of Health regeneration on him and his allys for 50% of his bonus in a 1200 radius, Xarofos
will also gain 1 bonus Movespeed for every 120 115 110 105 health lost.


damage reflected 10% 11% 12% 13%
Health bonus 8% 12% 16% 20%
Armor bonus 2 6 10 14
health regeneration bonus 20% 30% 40% 50%
health regeneration 0.2 per stacks
max stacks 11 22 33 44
stacks duration 2.4 2.5 2.6 2.7

talent level 20 upgrade Infuse Iron Body
increase damage reflected by 3%
increase health regeneration bonus by 20%
increase health regeneration per stack by 0.1
increase stack duration by 0.4

add a new modifier Iron Will
Xarofos cannot lose armor from debuff cause by the enemys but the enemys will alway do 10% of their damage in Pure on him with anything
and make his Health regeneration bonus Source Global and giving the same amount that Xarofos gets instead of reducing it by 50%, all
Movespeed slow or Armor lost debuff will Enrage Xarofos giving him 12 bonus armor with 15% increase movespeed and 0.85 reduce base
attack time for 4.5 seconds, this will have no coldown to proc again and if he get Enrage again while he is Enrage, he will Become
Pure Holy Iron, gaining 100% increase Healing effect and Health regeneration Source bonus for him self for 10 seconds, only proc every
40 seconds, refresh the duration of Iron Will when Pure Holy Iron proc and increase its duration by 4 seconds also increase his strenght
by 10%, And his magic resist by 15% of his total armor.

ULTIMATE R Titan Form
Xarofos Become a Titan of Iron gaining 125% Size but reducing his movespeed by 25%, While in Titan Form he will reduce all form of
debuff duration with Stun, Blinds, roots, Silence and healing effect reduction, he also gain increase health and Strenght but reducing
his Agility to 0 for the duration of Titan Form, he also gain 2 new spells that will replace his Iron Blast and Iron Charge (talents
will have no effect for those spells -Iron Blast and Iron Charge), Molten Steel will also be in effect while in Titan Form, having no
mana cost and gaining increase radius, armor and magic resist, he also gain some Stolx Mana regeneration While in Titan Form

Status Resistence 25% 40% 55%
bonus Health 400 800 1200
bonus Strenght 25 50 75
bonus Stolx regeneration 0.7 1.5 2.3
Molten Steel radius bonus 85 125 165
Molten Steel bonus armor 4 7 10
Molten Steel bonus magic resist 7% 11% 15%
